OL,3,CSwansea says goodbye to M&S after
OL,4,Cnearly a century on high street
OL,6,FSwansea shoppers have been left
OL,7,F"shocked" as they prepare to say
OL,8,Fgoodbye to a store that has been on
OL,9,Fits high street for nearly a century.
OL,11,FMarks & Spencer (M&S) will close its
OL,12,Fdoors for the final time on Saturday
OL,13,F(30 May).
OL,15,FOne shopper told ITV News that the
OL,16,Fclosure will leave the city centre
OL,17,Fempty.
OL,19,FShe said: "It's ridiculous, absolutely
OL,20,Fridiculous. We have nothing now in
OL,21,FSwansea, I won't come to town now."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
