OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780074357
OL,3,CSwansea says goodbye to M&S after
OL,4,Cnearly a century on high street
OL,6,FAnother customer agreed, saying: "It's
OL,7,Fabsolutely shocking. There's not many
OL,8,Fshops around here, and this is the
OL,9,Flast big store.
OL,11,F"It'll kill the town all together".
OL,13,FThe company explained that their
OL,14,Fdecision to shut its Swansea shop is
OL,15,Fdue to a new investment strategy.
OL,17,FIn a statement, M&S wrote: "Our M&S
OL,18,FSwansea city centre store will close
OL,19,Fon Saturday 30 May.
OL,26,@yD@\OU
