PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780074357
OL,3,CSwansea says goodbye to M&S after
OL,4,Cnearly a century on high street
OL,6,F"As previously announced, this
OL,7,Fdecision forms part of our plans to
OL,8,Freshape our store estate so we can
OL,9,Finvest in stores that better meet the
OL,10,Fneeds of our customers.
OL,12,F"We remain committed to serving
OL,13,Fcustomers in Swansea through our
OL,14,Fnearby stores and online, and are
OL,15,Fworking closely with Swansea Council
OL,16,Fand other local partners to explore
OL,17,Fopportunities for a future M&S
OL,18,Fpresence in the city."
OL,26,@zD@VO]
