CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780074357
OL,3,CSwansea says goodbye to M&S after
OL,4,Cnearly a century on high street
OL,6,FLeader of Swansea Council, Rob
OL,7,FStewart, said: "We are disappointed
OL,8,Fthat M&S choose to close the current
OL,9,Fstore before an alternative location
OL,10,Fcould be found.
OL,12,FThis would have avoided a gap in trade
OL,13,Ffor customers and employment for M&S
OL,14,Fstaff. However, we will continue to
OL,15,Fwork with M&S to find a new location
OL,16,Ffor a store in Swansea".
